---
import { business, company } from "../data/company";
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
    title="Privacy Notice | G2Labs"
    description="Privacy notice for g2labs.dev covering contact-form submissions, external links, and basic site operation."
>
    <section class="page-intro panel">
        <p class="eyebrow">Privacy notice</p>
        <h1>How G2Labs handles information shared through this site.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
            This notice applies to {company.site} and to inquiry submissions sent
            through the contact forms available on this site.
        </p>
    </section>

    <section class="panel panel-shell prose">
        <h2>Controller</h2>
        <p>
            The site is operated by <strong>{business.companyName}</strong>, an
            independent business based in {business.country}. Public business
            details are available through the CEIDG registry linked on the
            contact page.
        </p>

        <h2>What information may be collected</h2>
        <p>
            If you send an inquiry, G2Labs may receive the information you
            provide in the form, such as your name, email address, company,
            product stage, engagement type, technical stack, and the project or
            delivery details you choose to include.
        </p>
        <p>
            The site may also rely on standard hosting or service logs needed to
            deliver the website reliably.
        </p>
        <p>
            If you accept analytics, the site may load Google Analytics to
            collect aggregate usage information. If you decline analytics, the
            analytics script is not loaded by this site.
        </p>

        <h2>Why this information is used</h2>
        <p>
            Inquiry data is used only to review your request, respond to you,
            and discuss potential cooperation or follow-up technical questions.
        </p>

        <h2>Third-party services</h2>
        <p>
            When the contact form is active, submissions are sent through the
            configured Herotofu endpoint for form handling and may redirect to a
            site-hosted thank-you page after successful submission. The site may
            also be served through hosting infrastructure that processes
            technical request data required to operate the service.
        </p>
        <p>
            External links on this site may lead to third-party services such as
            LinkedIn, GitHub, Facebook, or the CEIDG public registry. Their own
            privacy policies apply when you use those services.
        </p>

        <h2>Cookies and local preferences</h2>
        <p>
            The site stores local preferences for the color theme and analytics
            consent in your browser. These choices are used to keep the selected
            experience across visits.
        </p>

        <h2>Retention</h2>
        <p>
            Inquiry information is retained only for as long as needed to answer
            the request, continue the conversation, or maintain basic business
            records connected to the inquiry.
        </p>

        <h2>Your choices</h2>
        <p>
            Do not send sensitive information through the general contact form
            unless it is genuinely necessary for the inquiry. If you want to ask
            about data handling related to a past inquiry, use the contact page
            to reach G2Labs directly.
        </p>

        <h2>Updates</h2>
        <p>
            This notice may be updated when the site, form handling, or legal
            requirements change.
        </p>
    </section>
</BaseLayout>
